CHICAGO - People in Chicago's Little Village neighborhood say they're concerned about women in their community going missing. In two recent cases, women reported missing were later found dead. A former youth coach and McKeesport teacher already in jail for alleged sexual abuse against children is facing more charges dating as far back as 2015. Eric Fairman faces new charges of endangering the welfare of children, indecent assault, unlawful contact with a minor, corruption of minors, and sexual assault by a sports official, volunteer or employee. ALEXANDRIA, Va. ‚Äì A former U.S. Department of State employee was sentenced today to 15 years in prison for engaging in illicit sexual conduct in a foreign place.
